article_title: Will You Buy Your Healthcare At Walmart?

article_metadata.description: Healthcare is becoming a retail business. The exchanges and other forces are making consumers responsible for choosing health plans and providers. Major retailers see this, and they are deepening their health care value add, becoming healthcare providers and more.
article_metadata.author: Todd Hixon
